{"tid":2429512,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「敗燈德政」屌打侵粉！華為太子女，美國放生機會大！！","createTime":"2021-03-02T11:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T00:40:46.000Z","uid":219635,"like":109,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"b4ae11d10694ab8d93b9688f7b58e4a880276886","tid":2429512,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:02:17.000Z","msg":"「蘋果」美國指孟晚舟涉嫌欺詐滙豐等銀行有關華為與香港空殼公司「星通技術」的關係，讓華為透過「星通技術」與伊朗交易，違反美國對伊朗禁運制裁。加拿大應美國要求，在2018年12月1日孟晚舟過境時在溫哥華機場拘捕她。美國一個多月後提出引渡要求。目前孟晚舟一方試圖推翻引渡要求。<br />\n<br />\n美國檢察官指孟晚舟說「星通技術」已賣給第三方，但實際上那第三方也由華為控制。<br />\n<br />\n達里奧指，<span class=\"red\">美國檢察官有關滙豐根據孟晚舟的陳述所決定的證據「誤導」，淡化了滙豐全球客戶關係經理對華為和「星通技術」關係的了解。達里奧因此要求推翻引渡案。   </span><br />\n<br />\n今輪聆訊一連五天在卑詩省最高法院進行，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">焦點包括美國前總統特朗普涉嫌干預引渡案及其他有關濫用程序的爭辯。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\">都估到放生華為要搵藉口，藉口就係「侵侵干預美國司法去拉華為，而家燈燈捍衛美國法治，釋放慢慢鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210302/YLDZESBZ5FCZZK4VQ2AMWBEECQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210302%2FYLDZESBZ5FCZZK4VQ2AMWBEECQ%2F&d=a689Ea%2B9Xr9H89nGruQQA8FcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=9198cead\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210302%2FYLDZESBZ5FCZZK4VQ2AMWBEECQ%2F&h=ec7e0d29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210302/YLDZESBZ5FCZZK4VQ2AMWBEECQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n賭局開始！<br />\n燈燈放生華為！捍衛法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n燈燈決定跟隨侵侵，放棄奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f6273ad97f4c39ebb5086a21300442b1fd7229","tid":2429512,"uid":219635,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:02:53.000Z","msg":"美豬左膠：燈燈要捍衛法治，拒絕侵侵濫捕！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd28919d5c4edda96e3aba4f3ef5dc2080b2f60b","tid":2429512,"uid":47080,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:04:14.000Z","msg":"班阻膠、愛登力去哂邊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1403916af5aa96676983178c648e037802688d35","tid":2429512,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:07:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0cace9bf73320956f7c499069bd43f47f8c4df1","tid":2429512,"uid":75461,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:10:29.000Z","msg":"左膠治國唔係假架喎，睇吓仲有幾多核彈級先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66942472321c26b4696de3028bbd223e70f23bdd","tid":2429512,"uid":19527,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:12:25.000Z","msg":"登粉日日比人binc點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3828e2210c5311dc14efa4e460bcbff3b7a1420","tid":2429512,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:13:08.000Z","msg":"文盲都識上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e88a54f84b85a0767cdd67c10a3145638e6d1cd1","tid":2429512,"uid":38316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1